	<module type="driver" id="sam.drivers.acc" caption="ACC - Analog Comparator Controller">
		<info type="description" value="summary">
			The Analog Comparator compares two voltages and the result of this
			comparison gives a compare output. The user can select a high-speed
			or low-power option. Additionally, the hysteresis level, edge detection
			and polarity are configurable.
		</info>
